msgctxt "33\t93\t60\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Hey, wait up."
msgstr "Ehi, aspettate."

msgctxt "166\t264\t98\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "You're just gonna leave without saying goodbye?"
msgstr "Ve ne andate senza neanche salutare?"

msgctxt "283\t387\t104\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"What's this about?\n"
"You two tryin' to start something again?"
msgstr ""
"Che succede?\n"
"Cercate di nuovo rogne, voi due?"

msgctxt "424\t526\t102\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "We just watched a playback of your performance."
msgstr "Abbiamo appena visto la registrazione della tua esibizione."

msgctxt "532\t666\t134\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"We couldn't just let you leave\n"
"without telling you this first..."
msgstr ""
"Non potevamo lasciarti andare\n"
"senza prima dirti questo..."

msgctxt "687\t743\t56\t　\t60ｆ以下です\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Just what are you up to?"
msgstr "Cosa avete in mente?"

msgctxt "744\t844\t100\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Nothing. We just have something to say."
msgstr "Niente. Abbiamo solo qualcosa da dirti."

msgctxt "931\t1091\t160\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"As much as I hate to admit it,\n"
"your performance really moved us."
msgstr ""
"Per quanto odi ammetterlo,\n"
"la tua esibizione ci ha davvero commosse."

msgctxt "1121\t1181\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "It was incredible."
msgstr "È stata incredibile."

msgctxt "1203\t1306\t103\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "It wasn't easy for us to come this far, either."
msgstr "Non è stato facile neanche per noi arrivare fin qui."

msgctxt "1316\t1366\t50\t　\t60ｆ以下です\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "So we understand."
msgstr "Quindi lo capiamo."

msgctxt "1367\t1526\t159\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"You must have practiced a lot\n"
"to be able to perform like that."
msgstr ""
"Devi esserti allenata un sacco\n"
"per riuscire a esibirti in quel modo."

msgctxt "1536\t1625\t89\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "It takes guts, no doubt about it."
msgstr "Ci vuole fegato, non c'è dubbio."

msgctxt "1644\t1699\t55\t　\t60ｆ以下です\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Girls..."
msgstr "Ragazze..."

msgctxt "1700\t1771\t71\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "That's all. See ya."
msgstr "Questo è tutto. Ci vediamo."

msgctxt "1873\t1933\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Thank you both for saying that!"
msgstr "Grazie per avermelo detto, ragazze!"

msgctxt "2020\t2199\t179\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"I don't think I could have given it my all"
"\n"
"if I wasn't facing off against you two."
msgstr ""
"Non credo che sarei riuscita a dare il massimo"
"\n"
"se non mi fossi scontrata con voi due."

msgctxt "2223\t2315\t92\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "So... So..."
msgstr "Quindi... Quindi..."

msgctxt "2358\t2419\t61\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "You really are clueless."
msgstr "Sei proprio un'ingenua."

msgctxt "2484\t2544\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Right, Azusa?"
msgstr "Vero, Azusa?"

msgctxt "2578\t2712\t134\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"You'll never make it in this world"
"\n"
"if something like that makes you cry."
msgstr ""
"Non ce la farai mai in questo mondo"
"\n"
"se una cosa del genere ti fa piangere."

msgctxt "2740\t2865\t125\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "But maybe that's part of your charm."
msgstr "Ma forse fa parte del tuo fascino."

msgctxt "2891\t3026\t135\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"Still, we're confident we're\n"
"gonna hit it big, just watch."
msgstr ""
"In ogni caso, siamo sicure che\n"
"faremo il botto, resta a guardare."

msgctxt "3047\t3107\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "I think so, too."
msgstr "Lo credo anch'io."

msgctxt "3294\t3362\t68\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Anyway, we should get going."
msgstr "Comunque, è meglio che andiamo."

msgctxt "3380\t3429\t49\t　\t60ｆ以下です\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "See you around."
msgstr "Ci si vede."

msgctxt "3430\t3507\t77\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Yeah. See you!"
msgstr "Sì. Ci vediamo!"

msgctxt "3594\t3710\t116\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"They're better kids than I thought they were.\n"
"Gotta say, they've really changed my opinion."
msgstr ""
"Sono ragazze migliori di quanto credessi.\n"
"Devo ammettere che mi hanno fatto proprio ricredere."

msgctxt "3740\t3800\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Mine too."
msgstr "Anche a me."

msgctxt "3809\t3869\t60\t　\t \t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Well, let's move."
msgstr "Bene, andiamo."

msgctxt "3891\t3987\t96\t　\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid ""
"We'll have a party when we get\n"
"back to the office. Sound good?"
msgstr ""
"Faremo una bella festa quando torneremo\n"
"in ufficio. Che ne dici?"

msgctxt "4000\t4060\t60\t　\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
msgid "Yes, ma'am!"
msgstr "Sissignora!"

